Golubev won 6-3, 6-3 against Teymuraz Gabashvili of Russia.

Meanwhile, Istomin had 14 aces in a 6-1, 6-1 rout of Poland's Jerzy Janowicz, a renowned big server who managed only two aces and lost his serve five times.

 

